title._content: Elliot Street School in Keene NH

description._content: TITLE Elliot Street School in Keene NH CREATOR Keene Camera Club SUBJECT Buildings - NH - Keene Schools - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION Photograph of "the Elliot Street School which was later replaced by Wheelock School." "The Elliot Street school was built in 1886 to replace the Main Street school building, which had been removed during the widening of Appian Way." "In 1916-17, the old Elliot School was rebuilt and expanded and renamed the Wheelock School in honor of Keene's wel-known naturalist."
